<td style="width: 21%; padding: 5px; border: 1px solid black; background-color: #EEEEEE;"><strong>事件编号：</strong>H25-001</td>
<td style="width: 58%; padding: 5px; border: 1px solid black;"><strong>事件类型：</strong>癸种一类 (异常残骸/已完全保管)</td>
<td style="padding: 5px; border: 1px solid black;"><strong>调查情况：</strong>未解決</td>
